    {
        "createdBy": 5,
        "createdDate": "2017-10-30T23:50:38.000+0000",
        "documentKey": "AIS-VAL-20",
        "fields": {
            "description": "<p>The formula for calculating breaking speed is derived from the motion equation:</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img align=\"middle\" alt=\"v squared minus v subscript 0 superscript 2 equals 2 a d\" class=\"Wirisformula\" data-mathml=\"&laquo;math xmlns=&uml;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&uml;&raquo;&laquo;msup&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;v&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;mn&raquo;2&laquo;/mn&raquo;&laquo;/msup&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;-&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;msubsup&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;v&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;mn&raquo;0&laquo;/mn&raquo;&laquo;mn&raquo;2&laquo;/mn&raquo;&laquo;/msubsup&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;=&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;mn&raquo;2&laquo;/mn&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;a&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;d&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;/math&raquo;\" role=\"math\" src=\"https://acceleratedsoftware.jamacloud.com/attachment/308/equation_20171030235655.png\" /></p>\n\n<p>v is the final speed of the vehicle which will be zero, vo will be the initial speed of the vehicle, a is the acceleration (or deceleration) of the vehicle and d is the breaking distance.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img align=\"middle\" alt=\"d equals fraction numerator negative v squared over denominator 2 a end fraction\" class=\"Wirisformula\" data-mathml=\"&laquo;math xmlns=&uml;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&uml;&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;d&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;=&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;mfrac&raquo;&laquo;mrow&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;-&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;msup&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;v&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;mn&raquo;2&laquo;/mn&raquo;&laquo;/msup&raquo;&laquo;/mrow&raquo;&laquo;mrow&raquo;&laquo;mn&raquo;2&laquo;/mn&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;a&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;/mrow&raquo;&laquo;/mfrac&raquo;&laquo;/math&raquo;\" role=\"math\" src=\"https://acceleratedsoftware.jamacloud.com/attachment/309/equation_20171030235721.png\" /></p>",
            "documentKey": "AIS-VAL-20",
            "globalId": "GID-55558",
            "name": "Detect accurate acceleration",
            "status": 293,
            "testCaseStatus": "PASSED",
            "testCaseSteps": [
                {
                    "action": "accelerate to 10 mph",
                    "expectedResult": "sensor reads 10 mph",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "action": "fully break to 0 mph",
                    "expectedResult": "sensor reads 0 pmh",
                    "notes": ""
                }
            ],
            "testRunResults": {
                "id": 0,
                "numBlocked": 0,
                "numFailed": 0,
                "numInProgress": 0,
                "numNotApplicable": 0,
                "numNotRun": 0,
                "numPassed": 1,
                "numTotalRuns": 1
            }
        },
