    {
        "createdBy": 5,
        "createdDate": "2017-10-30T23:24:13.000+0000",
        "documentKey": "AIS-VAL-21",
        "fields": {
            "description": "<p>To simulate dynamic angular velocity of a rolling automobile, the sensor is checked by the&nbsp;acceleration vector&nbsp;under static conditions. The acceleration vector of a fixed reference point on the automobile, moving within an inertial frame, consists of the acceleration of the origin of the body-fixed reference frame and the tangential and centripetal accelerations at the reference point arising from rotation of the the automobile</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img align=\"middle\" alt=\"begin mathsize 16px style stack A subscript p with rightwards arrow on top equals stack A subscript 0 with rightwards arrow on top plus omega with rightwards arrow on top cross times open parentheses omega with rightwards arrow on top cross times stack r subscript p with rightwards arrow on top close parentheses plus stack omega with times on top with rightwards arrow on top cross times r subscript p end style\" class=\"Wirisformula\" data-mathml=\"&laquo;math xmlns=&uml;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&uml;&raquo;&laquo;mstyle mathsize=&uml;16px&uml;&raquo;&laquo;mrow&raquo;&laquo;mover&raquo;&laquo;msub&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;A&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;p&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;/msub&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;&sect;#8594;&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;/mover&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;=&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;mover&raquo;&laquo;msub&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;A&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;mn&raquo;0&laquo;/mn&raquo;&laquo;/msub&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;&sect;#8594;&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;/mover&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;+&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;mover&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;&sect;#969;&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;&sect;#8594;&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;/mover&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;&sect;#215;&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;mfenced&raquo;&laquo;mrow&raquo;&laquo;mover&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;&sect;#969;&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;&sect;#8594;&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;/mover&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;&sect;#215;&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;mover&raquo;&laquo;msub&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;r&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;p&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;/msub&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;&sect;#8594;&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;/mover&raquo;&laquo;/mrow&raquo;&laquo;/mfenced&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;+&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;mover&raquo;&laquo;mover&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;&sect;#969;&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;&sect;#183;&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;/mover&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;&sect;#8594;&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;/mover&raquo;&laquo;mo&raquo;&sect;#215;&laquo;/mo&raquo;&laquo;msub&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;r&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;mi&raquo;p&laquo;/mi&raquo;&laquo;/msub&raquo;&laquo;/mrow&raquo;&laquo;/mstyle&raquo;&laquo;/math&raquo;\" src=\"https://acceleratedsoftware.jamacloud.com/attachment/306/equation_20171030233735.png\" /></p>",
            "documentKey": "AIS-VAL-21",
            "globalId": "GID-55559",
            "name": "Detect accurate angular velocity",
            "status": 293,
            "testCaseStatus": "PASSED",
            "testCaseSteps": [
                {
                    "action": "positioning the vehicle on a flat surface",
                    "expectedResult": "check against known static conditions are unchanged",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "action": "rotate the vehicle by 10 degrees",
                    "expectedResult": "compare acceleration force measured by the angular velocity sensor with the preset sensor value. A change should be noted",
                    "notes": ""
                }
            ],
